# Fonts & icons

Full checklist: `docs/static-site-standards.md` (Fonts & icons).

## Google Fonts

- Preconnect: `fonts.googleapis.com`, `fonts.gstatic.com` (`crossorigin`)
- Single `<link>` in `<head>` with `&display=swap`; variable fonts when available
- Only weights/styles in use; max 2 families (body + display)
- `&text=` for small glyph subsets (logo/hero)
- Optional: self-host woff2 + `<link rel="preload" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin>`
- System font stack always in `font-family` fallback chain

## Material Symbols

- Prefer Material Symbols (variable) over legacy Material Icons
- `&display=block`; limit FILL/wght/GRAD/opsz axes to what you need
- Decorative: `aria-hidden="true"`; icon-only controls: `aria-label`
- **Preferred for perf/a11y:** inline SVG from Google Fonts icon export (zero icon-font network)

## color-scheme

- `<meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark">` and CSS `color-scheme` on `:root`
